OL,3,C'It's not safe for us': Asylum seekers
OL,4,Cin Derby speak out after recent
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FTwo asylum seekers have told ITV News
OL,8,Fthey feel "unsafe" walking around the
OL,9,Fstreets amid recent protests across
OL,10,Fthe Midlands.
OL,12,FSpeaking in Long Eaton in Derbyshire,
OL,13,Fone man from Sudan and another from
OL,14,FEritrea both said they are fleeing
OL,15,Fprosecution and mandatory military
OL,16,Fservice, and that's why they are in
OL,17,Fthe country.
