OL,3,C'It's not safe for us': Asylum seekers
OL,4,Cin Derby speak out after recent
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FBoth men were inside hotels in
OL,8,FDerbyshire when anti-immigrant
OL,9,Fprotestors were protesting outside
OL,10,Fthis weekend in Long Eaton.
OL,12,FThey say that the experience has left
OL,13,Fthem often scared to go outside.
OL,15,FIt comes as Reform UK Leader Nigel
OL,16,FFarage has announced on Tuesday plans
OL,17,Fto deport 600,000 asylum seekers if
OL,18,Fthey were elected in parliament.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
