OL,7,FThe man from Eritrea said: "I still
OL,8,Fhave positive feelings, but it's not
OL,9,Fsafe for us to go beyond certain hours.
OL,11,F"There are times when you feel you
OL,12,Fmight get attacked by strangers. There
OL,13,Fare some groups of people who don't
OL,14,Fwant us in here. Basically, they don't
OL,15,Fwant us here".
OL,17,F"If things are going well in my own
OL,18,Fcountry, I don't want to stay here - I
OL,19,Fdon't want to be a burden on this
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
