OL,7,F"The people have to know we are not
OL,8,Fhere seeking free housing or
OL,9,Faccommodation. Being in the hotel, it
OL,10,Fhas its own stresses".
OL,12,F"I want to try and contribute to this
OL,13,Fbeautiful country and its people".
OL,15,FThe man fleeing Sudan said: "If my
OL,16,Fcountry becomes safe, I would want to
OL,17,Fgo back. It's not safe here; I cannot
OL,18,Fwalk on the street whenever I want.
OL,19,FIt's really hard for me.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
