OL,7,F"We don't choose to be here. We're
OL,8,Fhere because we have a problem and
OL,9,Fcan't go back".
OL,11,F"I'm a car mechanic, and if I get a
OL,12,Fchance here, I hope to continue as a
OL,13,Fcar mechanic."
OL,15,FWhen asked what he would like to do in
OL,16,Fthe future, the asylum seeker from
OL,17,FEritrea said: "I would love to do a
OL,18,Ftranslation job".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
