OL,7,FHe continued and said: "Even us as
OL,8,Frefugees we don't want to be in the
OL,9,Fhotel. We want to be outside, we want
OL,10,Fto learn the culture. We want to be
OL,11,FBritish citizens."
OL,13,F"We are not bad people."
OL,15,F"We need to have a job like them, but
OL,16,Fwe're not allowed to. We want to
OL,17,Fcontribute to this country. We want to
OL,18,Fcontribute to society."
OL,20,F"Every day we are slowly becoming more
OL,21,Fand more scared".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
