OL,7,FIn response to many people's concerns
OL,8,Fabout people moving to their
OL,9,Fcommunities, the men said they
OL,10,Funderstood their concerns, but
OL,11,Finsisted they are not a threat nor
OL,12,Fhere just for free accommodation.
OL,14,FOne said: "We hear them, we understand
OL,15,Fthem"
OL,17,F"We are not here seeking free housing
OL,18,Fand medication. We want to contribute
OL,19,Fto society".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
