OL,7,FOne of the asylum seekers said he no
OL,8,Flonger goes to the local church and
OL,9,Fthe other said that he doesn't
OL,10,Fvolunteer anymore because they feel
OL,11,Fincreasingly threatened.
OL,13,F"They don't know our history.
OL,15,F"What we want to tell them is hear us,
OL,16,Fhear our story"
