OL,3,C'It's not safe for us': Asylum seekers
OL,4,Cin Derby speak out after recent
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FSteve Cooke is the chairman of the
OL,8,FDerby Refugee Solidarity charity. They
OL,9,Fmeet twice a week and provide support
OL,10,Ffor hundreds of people who are mainly
OL,11,Fasylum seekers.
OL,13,FHe said the people the charity helps
OL,14,Fsupport are no different from anyone
OL,15,Felse.
OL,17,F"We just roll our sleeves up each week
OL,18,Fand get on with helping people that
OL,19,Fare in need, whoever that is and
OL,20,Fwherever they're from. We've got a
OL,21,Fsimple rule that we don't judge anyone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
