OL,7,F"I don't judge you or the cameraman or
OL,8,Fany of my friends and colleagues until
OL,9,FI know what your story is about your
OL,10,Fjourney through your life, which will
OL,11,Fprobably have lots of fun and laughter
OL,12,Fin it, but lots of pain and grief and
OL,13,Fsorrow. And it's the same for all of
OL,14,Fthese guys".
OL,16,FIn response to issues around asylum
OL,17,Fhotels, Home Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,18,Fsaid the government inherited a
OL,19,F'broken' system.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
