OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FShe said: "We inherited an asylum
OL,8,Fsystem in complete chaos with a
OL,9,Fsoaring backlog of asylum cases and a
OL,10,Fbroken appeals system with thousands
OL,11,Fof people in the system for years on
OL,12,Fend.
OL,14,F"That is why we are taking practical
OL,15,Fsteps to fix the foundations and
OL,16,Frestore control and order to the
OL,17,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
