OL,7,F"We are determined to substantially
OL,8,Freduce the number of people in the
OL,9,Fasylum system as part of our plan to
OL,10,Fend asylum hotels".
OL,12,FAmid Reform UK's plans called
OL,13,F'Operation Restoring Justice', the
OL,14,Fgovernment said they were "serious"
OL,15,Fabout solutions to immigration.
