OL,7,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "It makes him angry
OL,9,Ffrankly, because it's unfair on
OL,10,Fordinary working people who pay the
OL,11,Fprice from the cost of hotels to our
OL,12,Fpublic services struggling under the
OL,13,Fstrain.
OL,15,F"That's why we're taking the action we
OL,16,Fare, to recognise the strength of
OL,17,Ffeeling about this".
